query.alias: 客户端授权错误请求占比
query.q: M::`aliyun_acs_oss_dashboard`:(AVG(`AuthorizationErrorRate`) AS `客户端授权错误请求占比`) { `BucketName` = '#{BucketName}' and `account_name` = '#{account_name}' }

query.alias: 客户端其他错误请求占比
query.q: M::`aliyun_acs_oss_dashboard`:(AVG(`ClientOtherErrorRate_Value`) AS `客户端其他错误请求占比`) { `BucketName` = '#{BucketName}' and `account_name` = '#{account_name}' }

query.alias: 客户端超时错误请求占比
query.q: M::`aliyun_acs_oss_dashboard`:(AVG(`ClientTimeoutErrorRate_Value`) AS `客户端超时错误请求占比`) { `BucketName` = '#{BucketName}' and `account_name` = '#{account_name}' }

query.alias: 客户端资源不存在错误请求占比
query.q: M::`aliyun_acs_oss_dashboard`:(AVG(`ResourceNotFoundErrorRate`) AS `客户端资源不存在错误请求占比`) { `BucketName` = '#{BucketName}' and `account_name` = '#{account_name}' }

charts.name: 网络/服务端错误请求占比

query.q: M::`aliyun_acs_oss_dashboard`:(AVG(`ServerErrorRate_Value`) AS `服务端错误请求占比`) { `BucketName` = '#{BucketName}' and `account_name` = '#{account_name}' }
M::`aliyun_acs_oss_dashboard`:(AVG(`NetworkErrorRate_Value`) AS `网络错误请求占比`) { `BucketName` = '#{BucketName}' and `account_name` = '#{account_name}' }

query.alias: 客户端授权错误请求数
query.q: M::`aliyun_acs_oss_dashboard`:(AVG(`AuthorizationErrorCount`) AS `客户端授权错误请求数`) { `BucketName` = '#{BucketName}' and `account_name` = '#{account_name}' }

query.alias: 客户端其他错误请求数
query.q: M::`aliyun_acs_oss_dashboard`:(AVG(`ClientOtherErrorCount_Value`) AS `客户端其他错误请求数`) { `BucketName` = '#{BucketName}' and `account_name` = '#{account_name}' }

query.alias: 客户端资源不存在错误请求数
query.q: M::`aliyun_acs_oss_dashboard`:(AVG(`ResourceNotFoundErrorCount`) AS `客户端资源不存在错误请求数`) { `BucketName` = '#{BucketName}' and `account_name` = '#{account_name}' }
M::`aliyun_acs_oss_dashboard`:(AVG(`SyncRecv_Value`) AS `跨区域复制流入流量`) { `BucketName` = '#{BucketName}' and `account_name` = '#{account_name}' }
M::`aliyun_acs_oss_dashboard`:(AVG(`SyncSend_Value`) AS `跨区域复制流出流量`) { `BucketName` = '#{BucketName}' and `account_name` = '#{account_name}' }
